1.2.1.name: wordpress/dinky
1.2.1.description: Suitable for personal blogs that you can have blog and also visit card in home page yet. Several social icons to display your account links. Support RTL languages and ability to add different languages typography (English and Persian by defualt). This theme is responsive; means that action with screen size so it displayed good in tablet and mobile yet. Technologies used: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery. The proposed plugins compatible with this theme: wp-jalali, wp-pagenavi.
